      "writtenOn": "2026-03-28T20:51:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Please avoid this code duplication. Add an abstract super class for it. But see comments in GpgProcessConfiguration first. And if the info has to come in via the factory (see comment in the signature verifier), it\u0027ll be a constructor parameter anyway, and if only a single boolean, then it\u0027s perhaps not worth factoring it out.",
      "revId": "ced3f77ccfae96c05308c67eb0647e5aa0683c9d",
